      titulo: 'Exclusive specialisation',
      descripcion: 'We only do pladur (laminated plasterboard) and plaster — no general building, no subcontracted trades. We install exclusively Placo (Saint-Gobain), Knauf and Lafarge systems with full CE marking and manufacturer technical datasheets.',
